verbose_text: Baseline TC levels in the berberine and placebo groups were 226 +/- 15 and 220 +/- 18 mg/dL respectively; at the end of 3 months, there was a significant difference in the TC levels between groups (179 +/- 20 vs 195 +/- 15 mg/dL in the berberine and placebo groups respectively, P <.01).
